block content
  .container.py-5
    //- ---------- Page Intro ----------
    .row.mb-5
      .col-md-8.offset-md-2.text-center
        h1.display-4.mb-4 About RecipeShare
        p.lead.mb-4 We're passionate about bringing food enthusiasts together to share and discover amazing recipes from around the world.
        
    //- ---------- Three-column feature cards ----------
    .row.mb-5
      //- Share feature
      .col-md-4.mb-4
        .card.h-100.shadow-sm.text-center.p-4
          i.fas.fa-share-alt.fa-3x.text-primary.mb-3
          h3 Share
          p Create and share your favorite recipes with our community. Upload photos and detailed instructions to showcase your culinary creations.